{"tid":1192492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高院法官李瀚良聯署反修例　司法機構：馬道立已勸告避免再發生","createTime":"2019-06-08T12:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T12:45:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fc7895b04dd33e0e6ab6cad83222fff256bdef60","tid":1192492,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:36:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190608/s00001/261dcda80c6e1f50c24e8050c918803e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190608%2Fs00001%2F261dcda80c6e1f50c24e8050c918803e.jpg&h=fa6a7786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190608/s00001/261d52040f8a47732f81940c66c84cf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190608%2Fs00001%2F261d52040f8a47732f81940c66c84cf4.jpg&h=5d2e02b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有報章今日（8日）刊登香港大學畢業生要求撤回《逃犯條例》的聯署聲明，其中在1986年畢業校友的聯署名單中出現李瀚良的名字，與高等法院原訟法庭法官名字一樣。<br />\n<br />\n司法機構回應《明報》記者查詢表示，終審法院首席法官馬道立曾於今年5月29日指出，基於司法獨立及公正，法官應避免評論政治及其他具爭議的事宜。就有可能需要法庭處理的法律問題，法官更應避免發表意見。<br />\n<br />\n司法機構表示，馬道立隨後已提醒所有法官上述重要事情。就有法官參與聯署聲明，馬道立曾與有關法官討論，知悉其聯署是以個人名義、早於5月29日終審法院首席法官的聲明之前作出。<br />\n<br />\n馬道立勸告有關法官，將來應避免同類事情發生，有關法官表示同意首席法官的看法。"},{"pid":"9433613f42765ab5ef693e6644f4b6d1bb9f4d17","tid":1192492,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:36:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190608/s00001/1559994795536/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190608%2Fs00001%2F1559994795536%2F&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=64eb4e43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190608%2Fs00001%2F1559994795536%2F&h=48c4e62d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190608/s00001/1559994795536/</a>"},{"pid":"10f77cfa066fb8b7986a0b5c3781b74467ef26c8","tid":1192492,"uid":52230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:38:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化！不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即群擁而上集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n勿比機會警犬單獨拉走同伴！<br />\n<br />\n一切行動必須群體出發！ <br />\n<br />\nStick Together Team! 不要落單！<br />\n<br />\n6.9 GOGOGO!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔衝嘅人幫手拖住篤灰狗 <br />\n<br />\n衝嘅巴繼續上前！<br />\n<br />\n齊心！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b53e26d3867948b3dd74805fe6a2cd2f4b4bbff","tid":1192492,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:38:45.000Z","msg":"同中共講司法獨立？"},{"pid":"27e3eea2f86994f863245ceee283dfac3d080855","tid":1192492,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"反了反了"},{"pid":"64c05005bbb2bb9a44db68ce0194dd52cc4a6a64","tid":1192492,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37205ebf725aa63a5eab697ea8fdcab0afda45e7","tid":1192492,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:40:15.000Z","msg":"良心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6d66809a54e7ec2163441ad09f922bb6c28965","tid":1192492,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:45:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}